<strong>Comics and Document Use</strong>

A conversation with members of the <a href="http://www.thedclab.org/" target="_blank">Digital Cultures Lab</a> and members of the <a href="http://www.douglas.bc.ca/training-community-education.html" target="_blank">Douglas College Training Group</a> about the relationship between comics, document use, and essential skills.

